#

Vegan Buddha Bowl

35 min
$10
500 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Sesame (from tahini)

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeHigh Protein

Cuisine:

AmericanMediterranean

Course:

Main CourseSalad

Tags:

HealthyQuickEasy

Description

A colorful and nutritious bowl packed with fresh veggies, grains, and a creamy tahini dressing.

Ingredients

  • quinoa: 1 cup
  • chickpeas (canned, drained): 1 can (15 oz)
  • spinach (fresh): 2 cups
  • bell pepper (any color): 1, chopped
  • carrot (shredded): 1, large
  • avocado: 1, sliced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • tahini: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • garlic (minced): 1 clove
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
